data.title: New William S. Burroughs Book Sheds Light On The Literary Legend's Influence On Music
data.meta_description: Relying on a wealth of research and documents, Casey Rae deftly maps out how one of America's most controversial literary figures transformed the lives of many notable rock musicians.
